(117, 257, 11, 5, '2018-02-23 21:14:42', '125.161.105.102', NULL, '"Agnes Nauli S. W. Sianipar" <anyes07@gmail.com>', '"Dr. Henry Otgaar" <henry.otgaar@maastrichtuniversity.nl>', '"Tameka Romeo" <tameka.romeo@maastrichtuniversity.nl>, "Sara Landstrom" <sara.landstrom@psy.gu.se>', 'anyes07@gmail.com', '[PRoUSt]', 'Dear Dr. Henry Otgaar,\r\n\r\nThank you for submitting your manuscript to PRoUSt. After careful consideration, we feel that it has merit, but is not suitable for publication as it currently stands. Therefore, my decision is "Revisions required".  \r\n\r\nBased on the comments and evaluation of the reviewer, we invite you to submit a revised version of the manuscript that addresses the points made by the reviewer.  A Word file of the reviewed manuscript has been uploaded and attached to this e-mail.  Please use the file to start your revision.  Finally, we encourage you to submit your revision to PRoUSt within 14 days of the date of this decision.\r\n\r\nThank you.\r\n\r\nBest regards,\r\n\r\nDr. Agnes Sianipar\n________________________________________________________________________\r\nPsychological Research on Urban Society (PRoUSt)\r\nhttp://proust.ui.ac.id/'),
