(121, 257, 16, 1, '2018-02-27 17:58:35', '152.118.65.250', NULL, '"Psychological Research on Urban Society" <proust@ui.ac.id>', '"Prof. Cecilia Cheng" <ceci-cheng@hku.hk>', NULL, 'eflina@gmail.com, proust@ui.ac.id', '[PRoUSt] Editor Decision on your manuscript', 'Dear Prof. Cecilia Cheng,\r\n\r\nThank you for considering the Psychological Research on Urban Society as an outlet for your work.  I have received an expert review of your manuscript entitled "A Two-Dimensional Framework for Analyzing Facebook Use and Subjective Well-Being", and I have also read the manuscript independently of the reviewerâ€™s comments. Both the reviewer and I agree that the topic is important and is in line with our journalâ€™s theme. However, we also are in agreement that the manuscript still needs to be revised to meet the standard of scientific article. Below I include the excellent and detailed comments from our reviewer for your consideration to improve the manuscript.\r\n\r\nTo submit a revision, please login with your account http://proust.ui.ac.id\r\nwith your username and password. If you have any problem regarding this\r\nstep, please email us at proust@ui.ac.id.\r\n\r\nI would like to receive the revision within 14 days from the receipt of this\r\nletter. Please let me know if you would like to have additional time to revise the paper.\r\n\r\nYours sincerely,\r\n\r\nProf. Sri Hartati R. Suradijono, M.A., Ph.D\r\nEditor-in-Chief\r\nPsychological Research on Urban Society\r\n\r\nReviewerâ€™s comments:\r\n\r\nThis manuscript is well-written, and would be a good topic for this journal. However, the author needs to pay attention to some things to improve the paper:\r\n\r\n1. This paper needs a general introduction part that brings the audience clarity on the research questions and hypotheses. Perhaps authors need to explain more about previous research gap and the theoretical contributions from this study. Please also add the context of urban setting in the introduction.\r\n2. Figure 1 in the introduction is missing. Please add.\r\n3. In the method section- Participants, please add information on the SD of age. Another demographic characteristic of the participants, such as frequency of Facebook use, will be beneficial to add in this section. \r\n4. In the method section- Measures. The explanation about Facebook use and satisfaction were not detailed. Please explain more about the three subscales, the two sections, sample of items, and who developed the scale. For every measure in this study, please add the explanation about sample of items and the reliability of each measure. \r\n5. One of the objectives of this study was to develop and validate a new measure for assessing Facebook use and satisfaction. However there was no explanation about the validation testing of the new measure in the result section. In the first part of the result, please explain about the reliability and validity of the scale. \r\n6. The results and discussion section are combined. It is better to separate them and discuss thoroughly about the results. \r\n7. The conclusion section is missing.\n________________________________________________________________________\r\nPsychological Research on Urban Society (PRoUSt)\r\nhttp://proust.ui.ac.id/'),
