(194, 257, 32, 4, '2018-08-13 13:01:22', '114.124.213.146', NULL, '"Debora Eflina Purba" <eflina@gmail.com>', '"Martina Dwi Mustika" <martinadwimustika@gmail.com>', '"Rahadi Prabowo" <rahadi.prabowo@gmail.com>, "Bertina Sjabadhyni" <bert.pioui@yahoo.com>', NULL, '[PRoUSt] Editor Decision', 'Martina Dwi Mustika:\r\n\r\nWe have reached a decision regarding your submission to Psychological Research on Urban Society, "How a Leader Transforms Employeesâ€™ Psychological Empowerment Into Innovative Work Behavior".\r\n\r\nOur decision is: Resubmit\r\n\r\nDebora Eflina Purba\r\nUniversitas Indonesia\r\neflina@gmail.com\r\n\r\nReviewer''s comment: \r\nThe paper is written well and fairly straightforward. My biggest concern is that it does not articulate its contribution to the literature given existing literature on these variables already exist.  The contribution of the paper needs to be better articulated. However, the very simply hypothesis. Perhaps a different analysis with additional variables may make the paper more interesting.\n________________________________________________________________________\r\nPsychological Research on Urban Society (PRoUSt)\r\nhttp://proust.ui.ac.id/'),
