(1, 'en_US', 'reviewPolicy', '<p>The submitted manuscripts are first reviewed by an assigned editor. Every submitted manuscript which pass this step will be screened using iThenticate to identify any duplicated text or possible plagiarism before being sent to reviewers. This journal uses double-blind review process, involving in-country and international reviewers, to ensure the manuscript in review meets high quality standard. The acceptance criteria for all manuscripts submitted are the quality and originality of the research and its suitability with our readership. Final acceptance or rejection rests with the Editorial Board.</p>', 'string'),
